    <div class="recipe">
        <h2>Fish and Chips</h2>
        <p>Fish and chips is a popular British dish consisting of fried battered fish served with crispy fried potatoes.</p>
        <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>4 large potatoes, peeled and cut into fries</li>
            <li>2 cups all-purpose flour</li>
            <li>1 cup cold water</li>
            <li>4 white fish fillets (cod, haddock, etc.)</li>
            <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
            <li>Vegetable oil for frying</li>
            <li>Vinegar (optional)</li>
        </ul>
